constructor.t.sol
├─ when the cow protocol vault relayer is set to the zero address
│  └─ it should revert
└─ when the cow protocol vault relayer is not set to the zero address
   ├─ when the cow protocol settlement contract is set to the zero address
   │  └─ it should revert
   └─ when the cow protocol settlement contract is not set to the zero address
      ├─ it should set the cow protocol vault relayer
      ├─ it should set the cow protocol settlement contract
      ├─ it should emit a GPV2VaultRelayerSet event
      └─ it should emit a GPV2SettlementSet event
